name: "Ubuso 004"
description:
God has given you one face, and you make yourself another.

Can you remember the face of every person who passes you on the street? But you know they are human. So how do you know them? Does an ugly face equal an ugly person? How do your friends describe you? Think about it...

Our aim is to create an identity for people to identify without their faces.

Here is "Ubuso 004". Forget this face.
